item.description:
@system wrote:

You can change the XP from dummies, just search for what the text says when you click on a dummy to train, and then itll take you to a certain thing, in Testscape, it will be like 100* and then under it youll see a 300* (something like that.) Change those numbers to like… 10* and 30*, and you’re all set.
Don’t expect people to to searching for you, this section is for people who dont understand things and need help.
